Metadata.Title: The Doomslayer(fixed)
Metadata.Description: Go indoors/take close shoot/kill about 50 NPCs to let that ghost bullet bug disappearRestart/Replan mission will make the game crash,so you have to go menu then get in this contract again if you don't want that happenRemember bring a sniper rifle to kill that guy outside of hotel.If you don't want the game crash when scoring,just choose go-offline when it says disconnected,you can still get xp and score on leaderboard.
